# Secure Satellite Communication and IoT Environmental Monitoring System

## Overview

This project integrates Cisco Packet Tracer networking with ESP32 embedded systems to simulate a secure satellite communication and environmental monitoring system.

## Features

- Cisco Packet Tracer Network
- VLAN Segmentation
- ACL Security
- ESP32 Embedded System
- PIR Motion Detection
- Temperature & Humidity Monitoring
- IoT Integration

## Hardware

- ESP32
- PIR Motion Sensor
- DHT11 Sensor
- Breadboard
- LEDs

## Software

- Cisco Packet Tracer
- Arduino IDE

